title: Polls: Priyanka Gandhi finally joins Cong campaign
text:
Priyanka Gandhi finally joins Congress campaign for UP polls Priyanka Gandhi finally joins Congress campaign for UP polls Feburary 10, 2017 1 /8 Priyanka Gandhi finally joins Congress campaign for UP polls 
Ending speculation on whether she will campaign in Uttar Pradesh or not especially after being termed as a key figure in the pre-poll SP-Congress alliance, Congress on Friday confirmed that Priyanka Gandhi will campaign in her Rae Bareli constituency (TOI photo) All Comments () Be the first one to review. We have sent you a verification email. To verify, just follow the link in the message 2 /8 Sonia Gandhi to join the campaign trials too 
Also Congress president Sonia Gandhi is likely to campaign for party candidates on seats falling under Rae Bareli Lok Sabha constituency. Sonia and Priyanka's schedule has not yet been finalised. Amethi and Rae Bareli go to polls in the 4th and 5th phase of polling in the state on February 23 and 27 (TOI photo) All Comments ()
